<p>Vertex AI supports two types of embeddings models, text and multimodal.
This document describes how to create a text embedding using the Vertex AI <a href="https://cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/generative-ai/docs/model-reference/text-embeddings-api">Text embeddings API</a>.</p>
